column5: I was just wondering how they would look like. Might be interesting. Thanks.  Largemouth basshead with smallmouth body. Muskiehead with pike body. Brookiehead with splake body.
Unfortunately, the critters shown in the 'Name that Critter' series were forwarded to me as such, not manipulated by myself, Granny or Elly-Mae.
Thanks away Clamp-It. Maybe Terry will see this and be able to help? He good with this stuff. I am well awhere of the tiger muskie but I thought this would be more interesting.
